		<title>星巴克股價因獲利疲軟而大跌</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/starbucks-share-price-slumps-weaker-earnings</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
